ller noe annet de trengte, men etter hvert ble julebukkg\u00e5inga bare kos. S\u00e5nn som det beskrives i julesangen \u00abRomjulsdr\u00f8m\u00bb. Du vet, den som begynner med \u00abEn skulle v\u00f8ri fire \u00e5r i romjul\u2019n\u00bb. Du trenger ikke v\u00e6re fire \u00e5r for \u00e5 ha det artig som julebukk. G\u00e5 sammen noen venner, kle dere ut i voksenkl\u00e6r eller som nisser, og ta med en kurv. Pr\u00f8v ut julas snille godterijakt denne romjula!"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nisseposten"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "15ac4c9d0848d440bdaab8b56cce17b0db05d16f43a610d826110b4c459fd1cd"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-10-19T03:31:22.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Liker du Halloween? Da kommer du til \u00e5 like \u00e5 g\u00e5 julebukk ogs\u00e5."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1282558.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Julebukk1"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7f54d0fb0a90e6743d0a1186e2e80ae44ba013f6.jpg?58faf675"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "G\u00e5 julebukk! -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "7f54d0fb0a90e6743d0a1186e2e80ae44ba013f6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "nisseposten"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kle", "julebukk"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["romjulsdr\u00f8m", "halloween"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "nisseposten"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1282558.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Julebukk1"}, {"